es","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 7, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by a tree with dry leaves and he struck it with his staff, making the leaves fall. The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, the praise of Allah, the glorification of Allah, the declaration there is no God\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17576,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/14\/forgive-aisha-all-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":21768,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Forgiveness: O Allah, forgive Aisha for all her sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When I saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, with a cheerful face, I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, supplicate to Allah for me.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cO Allah, forgive Aisha for her past and future sins, in secret and in public.\u201d Aisha laughed so much\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25391,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/09\/salat-on-time-delayed-jamaah\/","url_meta":{"origin":21768,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Pray on time if congregation is delayed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to me, \u201cO Abu Dharr, how will you be if your leaders delay the prayer from its proper time, or let it die altogether?\" I said, \u201cWhat do you command me to do?\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10032,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/26\/treat-slaves-well-free-them\/","url_meta":{"origin":21768,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: Treat your slaves well, and free them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 26, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came from Khaybar with two young boys. The Prophet gave one of them to Ali ibn Abi Talib, and he said, \u201cDo not beat him. I have prohibited hitting the people of prayer, and I saw him praying.\u201d The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17071,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/01\/sujud-sajdah-darajah\/","url_meta":{"origin":21768,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: Each prostration rewarded by a degree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 1, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo servant prostrates for the sake of Allah but that Allah will raise his status by a degree and expiate one of his sins.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 388 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0630\u0631 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u